statements: SELECT * FROM user_activity_tracking;
SELECT user_id, activity_type, team_id FROM user_activity_tracking WHERE user_id = 100;
SELECT activity_type, activity_timestamp FROM user_activity_tracking WHERE team_id = 200 ORDER BY activity_timestamp DESC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS total_users, AVG(EXTRACT(epoch FROM interaction_duration)) AS avg_duration FROM user_activity_tracking;
SELECT user_id, activity_type, team_id, activity_timestamp FROM user_activity_tracking WHERE activity_type IN ('Login', 'Logout') ORDER BY activity_timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, activity_type, activity_timestamp FROM user_activity_tracking WHERE activity_type = 'login' AND team_id = 123 ORDER BY activity_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, activity_type, interaction_duration FROM user_activity_tracking WHERE user_id = 456 ORDER BY interaction_duration ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT activity_type, COUNT(*) as activity_count FROM user_activity_tracking GROUP BY activity_type HAVING activity_count > 100 ORDER BY activity_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_activity_tracking WHERE activity_timestamp BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' AND team_id IN (123, 456) ORDER BY activity_timestamp ASC LIMIT 20;
SELECT team_id, AVG(EXTRACT(epoch FROM interaction_duration)) as avg_duration FROM user_activity_tracking GROUP BY team_id HAVING avg_duration > 500 ORDER BY avg_duration DESC;
